<h1>The Abjad <Tempo> spanner</h1>

<subsection>

<p>
The Abjad <Tempo> spanner groups consecutive notes, rests, chords and skips under a common tempo marking.
</p>

</subsection>

<interface>
<attributes>
   <inherited> duration
   <local> tempo
</attributes>
<methods>
   <inherited> capture
   <inherited> copy
   <inherited> die
   <inherited> fracture
   <inherited> fuse
   <inherited> index
   <inherited> move
   <inherited> surrender
</methods>
<overloads>
   <inherited> __contains__
   <inherited> __getitem__
   <inherited> __len__
</overloads>
</interface>

<comments>

<p>
See the <Tempo> class in <code>tempo/spanner.py</code> for implementation details.
</p>

</comments>

